history.content: Well, it's not directly dependent on any lower-div but 61B would help a lot since you will be using Java mostly (not sure about this semester) and you will be using data structures in projects. The class workload is probably on the lower side of upper-divs - comparable to 188 I would say. Projects were solo and didn't take more than a couple days for the majority of the class.

Can someone who took it last semester give me thoughts on the class workload and whether it was dependent on any other lower division classes. I heard that they changed it up quite a bit compared to past semesters as they made the projects much more tedious and time consuming. Any feedback would be great. Thanks!
history.subject: CS 186 Experience
